ygData.messageBody:
about the gaurd killing topic from a few days ago i think it rocks! I
remember when I first came to fennin, before only being on rallos and vallon,

up. As for newboes getting killed the garud killers usually helpem.
Zanren lv 13 gnome of fennin ro
